New release, 0.3.5

  • Fixed resource filter to also filter on propellants used by engines & RCS

The problem seems to be that the wrong version of the ClickThroughBlocker is installed. I'm looking into that, but for now, use one of the following files:

KSP 1.4.5:  https://github.com/linuxgurugamer/ClickThroughBlocker/releases/download/0.1.7.1/ClickThroughBlocker-1.4.5-0.1.7.1.zip

KSP 1.5.1:https://github.com/linuxgurugamer/ClickThroughBlocker/releases/download/0.1.7.1/ClickThroughBlocker-1.5.1-0.1.7.1.zip

KSP 1.6.1 &  KSP 1.7.0:https://github.com/linuxgurugamer/ClickThroughBlocker/releases/download/0.1.7.1/ClickThroughBlocker-1.6.1-0.1.7.1.zip

If you installed by CKAN, install one of the above files manually AFTER you finish with CKAN.

 

Edit:  CKAN has been updated with the correct information.

Just an FYI, if I had been able to see the original log files when this first started, I could have fixed it sooner.  Please keep that in mind for the future.

 

With all this being done, please try reinstalling via CKAN and let me know the results.  If you still have problems, please provide the log file in a location which will allow normal web downloading.
